title: Print, "Paper Doll Costume with Dotted Pattern and Emerald Green Bows", 1876–80
medium: Lithograph, brush and watercolors on cream heavy wove paper
description: This cream-colored dress has a dotted pattern with emerald green bow accents.  The paper doll holds a parasol in her right hand. Both the back and front of this dress are depicted.

tombstone.epitaph:
Print, "Paper Doll Costume with Dotted Pattern and Emerald Green Bows", 1876–80.
1876–80. Lithograph, brush and watercolors on cream heavy wove paper. Gift of Grace Lincoln Temple. 1937-22-7.
